 <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_20">20</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_21">21</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_22">22</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_23">23</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_24">24</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_25" class="active">25</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_26">26</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_27">27</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211020220555/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Act/ch_28">28</a> 				</div>
